title: Chevrolet Corvette 427 Convertible Screensaver
description:
This screensaver include only High resolution wallpapers.
You can change everything by yourself in the screensaver settings.

Such as item order (Sequential, random and shuffle).
How long a image wait for another one.
Position of the images (Resize, stretch or do nothing).
100+ effects to view the next image. (Including the speed)
You can add your own playlist to the screensaver for your own music.
And much more.
You can see some screenshots and a video on: http://www.tuned-cars.net/index.php?template=screensaver_explain

The screensaver comes with a easy installer so you don't have to do anything, just run the .exe file in the torrent and click once on "next" and that's it your're done.

I hope you will enjoy the screensaver, and please come back for more stunning free tuned-cars screensavers.
